<table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=10>
<tr><td bgcolor="#363636">
<a name="razing_sword_of_skarlon"></a>
<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Razing Sword of Skarlon</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Skill: <a href="/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">2H Slash</a><BR>
Damage per second - 12.75<BR>
Damage 25 - Delay 40<BR>
Weight: 9.5 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/paladin/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">PAL</a>, <a href="/shadow_knight/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">SHD</a>, <a href="/warrior/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">WAR</a><BR>
Effect: <a href="http://www.maximumeq.com/spells/individual/serpent_sight.shtml?spellID=334">Serpent Sight</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
</font>
Dropped in Solusek B by Warlord Skarlon.<BR>

